Enjoy the unique duo of Naruto and Pikachu in this 4K live wallpaper, with a clock and Google search bar on your new tab.

Light up your Chrome new tab with the playful and unexpected pairing of Naruto and Pikachu in this 4K live wallpaper. Featuring vibrant visuals of these iconic characters, the extension combines the energy of the Naruto universe with Pikachu’s electric charm. The minimalist design includes a clean clock and a Google search bar, delivering both style and functionality. Whether you’re a fan of anime, Pokémon, or creative crossovers, this live wallpaper brings a fun and dynamic twist to your browsing experience.
